title: Chat Message Lifecycle
type: sequence
phase: CORE
prd_section: "5. AI agent architecture — OpenClaw conversation flows"
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant WebApp as mdeai.co<br/>(React)
    participant Router as ai-router<br/>(Gemini Lite)
    participant Chat as ai-chat<br/>(Gemini Flash)
    participant Rentals as rentals<br/>(Edge Fn)
    participant Hermes as Hermes Agent<br/>(Claude via OpenRouter)
    participant DB as Supabase<br/>(PostgreSQL)
    participant OpenClaw as OpenClaw<br/>(WhatsApp)

    Note over User,OpenClaw: Web Channel Flow
    User->>WebApp: Types message in FloatingChatWidget
    WebApp->>Router: POST /ai-router<br/>{message, conversation_id}

    Router->>Router: Classify intent (Gemini Lite)
    Router-->>WebApp: {intent: RENTAL_SEARCH, confidence: 0.85}

    alt intent = RENTAL_SEARCH
        WebApp->>Chat: POST /ai-chat<br/>{message, intent, context}
        Chat->>Chat: Build system prompt<br/>(concierge agent)

        Chat->>Rentals: Tool call: search_apartments<br/>{budget, neighborhood, amenities}
        Rentals->>DB: SELECT with PostGIS + filters
        DB-->>Rentals: Matching apartments[]
        Rentals-->>Chat: Structured results

        Chat->>Chat: Format response with<br/>property cards + explanations
        Chat-->>WebApp: SSE stream:<br/>text + property_cards[]
        WebApp-->>User: Renders chat message<br/>+ inline listing cards

    else intent = SCHEDULE_SHOWING
        WebApp->>Chat: POST /ai-chat<br/>{message, intent, listing_id}
        Chat->>DB: Check host availability<br/>(showings table)
        DB-->>Chat: Available slots[]
        Chat-->>WebApp: SSE: "Available: Thu 2pm, Fri 10am"
        User->>WebApp: Selects Thursday 2pm
        WebApp->>Chat: POST /showing-create<br/>{listing_id, slot, lead_id}
        Chat->>DB: INSERT showings (status=proposed)
        Chat->>OpenClaw: Notify host via WhatsApp
        OpenClaw-->>Chat: Delivery confirmed
        Chat-->>WebApp: SSE: "Showing scheduled! Calendar invite sent."

    else intent = GENERAL
        WebApp->>Chat: POST /ai-chat<br/>{message, intent}
        Chat->>Chat: Concierge response<br/>(neighborhood tips, FAQ)
        Chat-->>WebApp: SSE stream: text response
    end

    WebApp->>DB: Log to conversations + messages
    WebApp->>DB: Log to ai_runs<br/>(agent, tokens, duration)

    Note over User,OpenClaw: WhatsApp Channel Flow
    User->>OpenClaw: WhatsApp message<br/>(via Infobip webhook)
    OpenClaw->>Router: Classify intent
    Router-->>OpenClaw: {intent, language: "pt"}
    OpenClaw->>Chat: Forward with channel=whatsapp
    Chat-->>OpenClaw: Response + property cards
    OpenClaw->>OpenClaw: Format for WhatsApp<br/>(inline images, quick replies)
    OpenClaw-->>User: WhatsApp response<br/>with property carousel

    Note over Chat,DB: Confidence < 0.3 triggers human handover
    Chat->>Chat: confidence = 0.2
    Chat->>DB: Flag conversation for escalation
    Chat-->>WebApp: "Let me connect you with our team..."
    Chat->>OpenClaw: Alert ops team
